        "title": "Why Choose QuickBee Wholesale?",
        "content": "<ul><li><strong>Competitive Pricing:</strong> Volume discounts starting from just 10 units. The more you order, the more you save—up to 40% off retail pricing</li><li><strong>Flexible Terms:</strong> 30, 45, or 60-day payment terms available. No minimum order requirements</li><li><strong>Fast Fulfillment:</strong> Same-day dispatch for orders placed before 12 PM. Nationwide delivery within 2-3 business days</li><li><strong>Dedicated Support:</strong> Assigned account manager for personalized service and order management</li><li><strong>Bulk Customization:</strong> Special packaging, branding options, and custom product bundles available</li><li><strong>Real-time Inventory:</strong> Live stock visibility through our wholesale portal</li></ul>",
