        "content": "<p>We serve retailers and businesses across multiple sectors. Our most popular bulk ordering categories include:</p><ul><li><strong>Electrical Equipment:</strong> Wires, cables, switches, circuit breakers, distribution boards</li><li><strong>Installation Materials:</strong> Pipes, conduits, couplers, fasteners for installers</li><li><strong>Lighting Solutions:</strong> LED lights, fixtures, bulbs, and smart lighting systems</li><li><strong>Power Tools & Equipment:</strong> Essential tools for electricians and contractors</li><li><strong>Safety Gear:</strong> PPE, safety equipment, and protective devices</li><li><strong>Renewable Energy:</strong> Solar panels, inverters, batteries for sustainable projects</li></ul><p><strong>Not finding what you need?</strong> Contact our sales team for custom bulk orders and special requests.</p>",
