: 700; margin: 0 auto 16px;\">4</div><h3 style=\"font-size: 16px; margin-bottom: 12px; font-weight: 700; color: #222;\">Get Delivery</h3><p style=\"color: #666; margin: 0;\">Fast dispatch with tracking. Free shipping on orders over Rs 50,000</p></div></div></div>"
